Jack is a newly appointed traffic policeman. Due to his inexperience, he hopes to have a traffic simulator to simulate the local traffic situation to help him get familiar with his work.

Michael is a new resident who has just moved to the local area. He has his own car, but he is not familiar with the local traffic, so he hopes to have a traffic simulator to help him get familiar with the local traffic sections.

James is preparing for his driving test. He hopes to have a traffic simulator to simulate the driving mode in different traffic sections to help him complete the test.

Tom is a new immigrant to Australia. He is not familiar with the traffic mode in Australia, so he hopes to have a traffic simulator to help him adapt to the traffic mode in Australia.
